3. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the technical aspects of breaching a medical training mannequin, which involves understanding the system and control mechanisms of the device. This falls under the purview of systems and control.

4. cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the technical aspects of breaching a medical training mannequin, which involves understanding the software components of the device. This falls under the purview of software engineering.
